question: Display magicians and mimes that performed in Times Square street in New York.
sql_query1:
SELECT PERFORMERS.NAME 
FROM PERFORMERS
WHERE (PERFORMERS.GENRE = "Magic" OR PERFORMERS.GENRE = "Mime") AND PERFORMERS.STREET_LOCATION = "Times Square, New York"
sql_query2:
SELECT PERFORMERS.NAME 
FROM PERFORMERS
WHERE PERFORMERS.GENRE = "Magic" OR PERFORMERS.GENRE = "Mime" AND PERFORMERS.STREET_LOCATION = "Times Square, New York"
interpretation1: Which magicians performed in Times Square street in New York and which mimes performed on the same street?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all magicians and also provide a list of mimes that performed in Times Square street in New York.
